<h1 id="api" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#api"><span>API</span></a></h1>
<h4 id="button-props" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#button-props"><span>Button props</span></a></h4>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>名称</th>
<th>类型</th>
<th>默认值</th>
<th>说明</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>type</td>
<td><code v-pre>'default' | 'primary' | 'danger' | 'wrong' | 'success'</code></td>
<td><code v-pre>default</code></td>
<td>按钮的类型，显示不同的颜色</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>size</td>
<td><code v-pre>'small' | 'middle' |'large'</code></td>
<td><code v-pre>middle</code></td>
<td>按钮的尺寸</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>disabled</td>
<td><code v-pre>boolean</code></td>
<td><code v-pre>false</code></td>
<td>按钮是否禁用</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>dash</td>
<td><code v-pre>boolean</code></td>
<td><code v-pre>false</code></td>
<td>按钮是否显示虚线</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>ghost</td>
<td><code v-pre>boolean</code></td>
<td><code v-pre>false</code></td>
<td>按钮是否显示幽灵态</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>loading</td>
<td><code v-pre>boolean</code></td>
<td><code v-pre>false</code></td>
<td>按钮是否显示loading图标</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>onClick</td>
<td><code v-pre>(e: MouseEvent) =&gt; void</code></td>
<td><code v-pre>undefined</code></td>
<td>按钮点击回调函数</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
